default(TIC 26)
default&#xa0;defaultACRE is the national charity supporting rural community action through its founder members, the Rural Community Councils (RCCs) across England. The 38 RCCs are independent local development agencies, based at county level, addressing social, economic and e
defaultnvironmental challenges in rural areas. They provide help, support and advice for community-led action in rural areas throughout England.  
